    {
      "id": "mem_overlook-veld-001-phi-encryption-disconnected",
      "content": "CRITICAL: PHI encryption service (phiEncryptionService.js) exists with full AES-256-GCM implementation but has ZERO production callers. All PHI stored in plaintext. Planet X finding — the gravitational pull of the service's existence masks that it's disconnected. The service gives false assurance during audits because it exists, but no code path actually invokes it.",
