    {
      "id": "mem_overlook-veld-002-mfa-bypass",
      "content": "CRITICAL: MFA check in adminAuthService.js:156-165 has empty catch{} block — MFA failure is non-fatal, login proceeds without second factor. Also: MFA bypassed entirely when import.meta.env.DEV is true (line 167). This means in development builds, MFA is completely skipped, and in production, MFA exceptions are silently swallowed. An attacker who triggers an exception in the MFA flow gets in without a second factor.",
      "type": "Discovery",
      "importance": 0.98,
      "created_at": "2026-03-30T00:00:00.000Z",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-30T00:00:00.000Z",
