    {
      "id": "mem_overlook-veld-003-edge-function-jwt",
      "content": "HIGH: 12 edge functions have verify_jwt=false in supabase/config.toml:371-423. Each has internal auth mechanisms (bridge tokens, HMAC) but the attack surface is large. JWT verification disabled at the gateway means every one of these functions must independently validate every request — a single missed check in any of 12 functions creates an unauthenticated endpoint.",
