    {
      "id": "mem_overlook-veld-004-phi-audit-gaps",
      "content": "HIGH: PHI audit logging exists in only 18 files. 10 admin pages access patient data without any audit trail: Appointments, Calendar, MrDiagnosis, QuestionnaireResponses, GenerateLetter, and others. HIPAA requires audit logging for all PHI access. Over a third of PHI-accessing pages have no audit trail — this is a compliance gap, not just a best-practice miss.",
