    {
      "id": "mem_overlook-veld-005-fractal-pattern",
      "content": "STRUCTURAL: Core fractal pattern confirmed for Veld: Auth>State>Fetch>Filter>Render. Holds at macro level (100% admin-page wrapper compliance). Breaks at meso level (no shared DataTable component, 76 inline table implementations). Breaks at micro level (20 services return {error}, 26 throw exceptions, mixed error handling within single files). The fractal breaks at meso and micro indicate the codebase grew through copy-paste rather than abstraction — common in rapid medical software development.",
